## Summer Staff

Join our team for the best summer job ever! Positions include cabin counselors, lifeguards, recreation leaders, worship leaders, photography and videography, craft leaders, and LIT counselors.

- Ministry experience and spiritual growth
- Lifelong friendships with fellow staff
- Room, board, and stipend provided

{% ctaButton label="View Summer Staff Positions" href="/summer-staff" variant="inverse" size="lg" textColor="secondary" /%}
