## Leaders in Training

Our LIT program is a unique 2-week servant leadership experience for students ages 15–17. Grow in faith, develop leadership skills, and make a real impact on campers' lives while serving alongside summer staff.

- For students ages 15–17
- Hands-on leadership development
- Serve alongside staff and grow in faith

{% ctaButton label="Learn About LIT" href="/work-at-camp-leaders-in-training" variant="inverse" size="lg" textColor="primary" /%}
